title: Rutgers coach Kyle Flood press conference: LIVE updates
text:
Comments 
PISCATAWAY â€” We have questions , we'll find out if Kyle Flood has answers. 
The Rutgers coach is scheduled to hold a press conference at 12 p.m. on Monday. It will be Flood's first meeting with the media since his three-game suspension was issued on Sept. 16 after he violated a university compliance policy. 
Flood will undoubtedly face many questions about his actions that led to the suspension as well other issues that have arisen during his university-imposed media ban. 
Will Flood offer specifics? Or will he try to direct the focus to going "1-0" against Indiana on Saturday ? We'll find out shortly. 
Keep it right here on NJ.com as Keith Sargeant, Steve Politi and I report live from the press conference.
